<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-29 01:44 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8481 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r s BC-GEN-WALL-COLUMN-LADN     05-29 0686
