 &HT;    Boys in the band
 &HT;    By Staff Reports
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA -
</P>
<P>
   'N Sync (left) has moved on after visiting Atlanta this month,
but you can keep the boys here forever _ on your Windows computer
screen. Go to www.mycometcursor.com and change your cursor into a
picture of Joey, Lance, JC, Justin or Chris. Sorry, this won't work
on a Mac.
