Open 5 a.m. to 9 p.m. but good bet for breakfast. A thick shake is
$2.25; three-egg omelets are $2.95 to $5.95. Sandwiches are $2.50
to $4.95. Dinners include chicken croquettes ($5.95) and
batter-fried haddock ($8.95).
</P>
<P>
   The Birches Resort, Post Office Box 41, Rockwood, Maine 04478;
