   OLD-TEACHER (Los Angeles) _ Eleanor Bralver is one of the
nation's oldest teachers, but age hasn't mellowed this 86-year-old
health educator. She teaches five classes a day at Sylmar High
School and still finds the energy to march with the teachers union.
By Erik Nelson. (Will move in the ``a'' national and ``n''
