<HEADLINE>
KNICKS EDGE PACERS, 91-89 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Repeating to add photo note) 
 (ART ADV: Photos _ NYT18,19 _ are being sent to NYT photo clients.
Nonsubscribers can purchase one-time rights by calling 888-603-1036
or 888-346-9867.)  By SELENA ROBERTS   
